Cheetor:




Cheetor woke with a turning head. He was dizzy and weak. He mumbled, "Ow, 
what hit me?" He lifted his head, looking around at an interior of a room. 
He looked down and saw a green glow mark on his side.

He remembered now. He was caught spying on two Preds, Stingtra and 
Quickstrike. He forgot how mean that son of a snake was. One crazy on two. 
He remembered how the sparks flew when he fired a shot before the little 
thing jumped on him.

On primus! Where was he? Cheetor sat up.
